.il/index.php?title=%D7%92%D7%9F_%D7%99%D7%A9%D7%A8%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A0%D7%95%D7%95%D7%94_%D7%99%D7%A2%D7%A7%D7%91&amp;action=edit&amp;editintro=%D7%AA%D7%91%D7%A0%D7%99%D7%AA%3A%D7%A7%D7%A6%D7%A8%D7%9E%D7%A8%2F%D7%94%D7%A8%D7%97%D7%91%D7%94%2F%D7%9E%D7%95%D7%A1%D7%93%D7%95%D7%AA+%D7%95%D7%90%D7%A8%D7%92%D7%95%D7%A0%D7%99%D7%9D\">להרחיב אותו</a></span></b>.</div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413091639\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.030 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.259 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 107/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4456/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 340/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/100\nExpensive parser function count: 1/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  180.673      1 -total\n 64.41%  116.378      1 תבנית:קצרמר\n 51.37%   92.820      1 תבנית:קצרמר/קוד\n 23.87%   43.129      2 תבנית:חב&quot;ד_און_ליין\n 16.08%   29.046      1 תבנית:רווח_קשיח\n 11.54%   20.846      2 תבנית:אינפו\n 10.36%   18.720      1 תבנית:קצרמר/נושא_נוסף\n  4.96%    8.960      2 תבנית:קטגוריה_בתבנית\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key chabadped_1-infopedia_:pcache:idhash:86936-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413091639 and revision id 791277. Rendering was triggered because: diff-page\n -->\n</div>"
